16 Agricultural Practices.
17 § 4632. FARM SECURITY SPECIAL FUND
18 (a) There is established the Farm Security Special Fund to be administered
19 by the Secretary of Agriculture, Food and Markets and that shall be managed
20 in accordance with 32 V.S.A. chapter 7, subchapter 5. The Fund shall consist
21 of:
