5 or private weather or satellite date or models.
6 (4) Losses reimbursable by a grant under this section include:
7 (A) wages or compensation;
8 (B) replacement of lost income from destroyed crops or impacted
9 livestock;
10 (C) debt payments or other ongoing expenses;
11 (D) costs of replanting;
12 (E) livestock feed replacement costs;
13 (F) infrastructure or equipment repair and replacement;
14 (G) repair of farm roads and roads necessary to access farms; or
15 (H) other losses as determined by the Secretary after consultation
16 with the Review Board.
